OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773069077
OL,3,CPolice investigating car shooting in
OL,4,CYork
OL,6,FPolice in York are investigating after
OL,7,Fa man shot a gun at a parked car in
OL,8,Fthe Tang Hall area last night.
OL,10,FThe unknown suspect walked up to the
OL,11,Funoccupied car and the fired the gun,
OL,12,Fwhich was outside an address on
OL,13,FStarkey Crescent, at around 9.25pm on
OL,14,FSaturday, 7 March.
OL,16,FHe then ran from the scene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
