OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773069077
OL,3,CPolice investigating car shooting in
OL,4,CYork
OL,6,FNorth Yorkshire Police have confirmed
OL,7,Fthat no-one has been harmed and it is
OL,8,Fbelieved to have been a targeted
OL,9,Fincident, with no threat to the wider
OL,10,Fcommunity.
OL,12,FThey added: "We know that this will
OL,13,Fcause concern and fear among residents.
OL,15,F"We are carrying out reassurance
OL,16,Fpatrols in the area while the
OL,17,Finvestigation continues.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
