PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773069077
OL,3,CPolice investigating car shooting in
OL,4,CYork
OL,6,F"Forensic and house-to-house enquiries
OL,7,Fare taking place, and CCTV, doorbell,
OL,8,Fand dashcam footage is being collated
OL,9,Fand examined to help identify the
OL,10,Fsuspect.
OL,12,F"We are appealing for witnesses to
OL,13,Fcome forward and those with any
OL,14,Frelevant recorded footage who have not
OL,15,Fyet assisted the police."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/3
